<article>
  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you should have any questions about our club, website, or club runs please feel free to check out our forum or drop us an email to contact one of our club officers. HDOR meetings are held on the last Tuesday of each month at 7:00pm. We meet at Smoky Mountain Pizza in Meridian 980 East Fairview Ave. All are welcome to attend, come in early and enjoy some great food and conversation. Keep in mind we all have full time jobs and families so please be patient on email replies.
